OL,6,FA retired civil servant suffered fatal
OL,7,Fhead injuries when she was blown over
OL,8,Fby a search and rescue helicopter
OL,9,Flanding at a hospital, an inquest jury
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FJean Langan, 87, had attended
OL,13,FDerriford Hospital in Plymouth, Devon,
OL,14,Fto have a hearing aid fitted and was
OL,15,Fwalking with her niece back to their
OL,16,Fcar in the hospital car park on 4
OL,17,FMarch 2022.
