OL,3,CPensioner died after being blown over
OL,4,Cby landing helicopter, jury told
OL,6,FHe said: "This inquest concerns the
OL,7,Fdeath of Mrs Jean Langan at Derriford
OL,8,FHospital on 4 March 2022.
OL,10,F"Shortly before her death, Mrs Langan
OL,11,Fwas in the hospital car park. A search
OL,12,Fand rescue helicopter carrying a
OL,13,Fpatient was coming into land at the
OL,14,Fnearby hospital helipad.
OL,16,F"Mrs Langan was blown over by the
OL,17,Fdownwash, that is the fast-moving air
OL,18,Fthat was created by the helicopter
OL,19,Flanding."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
