OL,3,CPensioner died after being blown over
OL,4,Cby landing helicopter, jury told
OL,6,FMr Arrow said the incident had been
OL,7,Finvestigated by the Air Accidents
OL,8,FInvestigation Branch (AAIB), which
OL,9,Fpublished a report.
OL,11,FHe told jurors that they would not be
OL,12,Finvestigating matters the AAIB had
OL,13,Falready examined, meaning there would
OL,14,Fbe no evidence from witnesses
OL,15,Fconcerning when Mrs Langan was injured.
OL,17,FThe coroner read a statement provided
OL,18,Fby Mrs Langan's family, who attended
OL,19,Fthe hearing which began at Devon
OL,20,FCounty Hall in Exeter on Monday.
