OL,3,CPensioner died after being blown over
OL,4,Cby landing helicopter, jury told
OL,6,FThey described their shock at her
OL,7,F"sudden and violent death" and said
OL,8,FMrs Langan was an important part of
OL,9,Ftheir family.
OL,11,F"Jean was the most senior member of
OL,12,Four family," they told the inquest.
OL,13,F"She had always been there for all of
OL,14,Four lives. The violent manner of her
OL,15,Fdeath has affected us all.
OL,17,F"She would have hated the publicity
OL,18,Fthat the circumstances surrounding her
OL,19,Fdeath have generated. As a result, she
OL,20,Flost the quiet dignity that she would
OL,21,Fhave chosen."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
