OL,3,CPensioner died after being blown over
OL,4,Cby landing helicopter, jury told
OL,6,FThe statement described how Mrs Langan
OL,7,F"doted" on the children in her family,
OL,8,Fincluding her three grandchildren.
OL,10,FIt said she had lived in her home for
OL,11,Fmore than 30 years, following her
OL,12,Fretirement from the Civil Service
OL,13,Fwhere she was renowned for her
OL,14,F"efficiency".
OL,16,F"She was always on the go," Mrs
OL,17,FLangan's family said, describing her
OL,18,Fas an expert knitter who walked the
OL,19,Ffamily's dog every day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
