OL,3,CPensioner died after being blown over
OL,4,Cby landing helicopter, jury told
OL,6,F"Jean was elderly and we knew that one
OL,7,Fday we would lose her. However, the
OL,8,Fmanner of her death has affected us
OL,9,Fimmensely. Jean was doing nothing
OL,10,Fwrong."
OL,12,FThe inquest jury watched CCTV footage
OL,13,Ffrom the hospital car park, which
OL,14,Fshowed people walking next to the wall
OL,15,Fof the helipad.
OL,17,FThey were seen falling to the ground
OL,18,Fas the search and rescue helicopter
OL,19,Fcame to land on the helipad.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
