OL,3,CPensioner died after being blown over
OL,4,Cby landing helicopter, jury told
OL,6,FDr Amanda Jeffery, a Home Office
OL,7,Fpathologist, told the inquest that Mrs
OL,8,FLangan sustained "significant" head
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FShe said: "Mrs Langan had attended a
OL,12,Froutine audiology appointment at
OL,13,FDerriford Hospital with her niece and
OL,14,Fwas returning to their parked car when
OL,15,Fa helicopter came into land.
OL,17,F"Mrs Langan was swept off her feet,
OL,18,Fcausing her to fall backwards onto the
OL,19,Fground."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
