OL,6,FDr Jeffery said Mrs Langan died about
OL,7,Fthree and a half hours after the
OL,8,Fincident, with the medical cause of
OL,9,Fher death given as a head injury.
OL,11,FThe inquest, which is due to last for
OL,12,Ffive days, continues.
